C</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/NeilSculthorpe.html">Neil Sculthorpe</a> (<a href="https://2023.splashcon.org/committee/sle-2023-program-committee">PC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/TamásSzabó.html">Tamás Szabó</a> (<a href="https://2023.splashcon.org/committee/sle-2023-program-committee">PC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/MauricioVeranoMerino.html">Mauricio Verano Merino</a> (<a href="https://2023.splashcon.org/committee/sle-2023-program-committee">PC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/ManuelWimmer.html">Manuel Wimmer</a> (<a href="https://2023.splashcon.org/committee/sle-2023-program-committee">PC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/VadimZaytsev.html">Vadim Zaytsev</a> (<a href="https://2023.splashcon.org/committee/sle-2023-program-committee">PC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/PhilippZech.html">Philipp Zech</a> (<a href="https://2023.splashcon.org/committee/sle-2023-program-committee">PC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/LuísEduardodeSouzaAmorim.html">Luís Eduardo de Souza Amorim</a> (<a href="https://2023.splashcon.org/committee/sle-2023-program-committee">PC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/LThomasvanBinsbergen.html">L. Thomas van Binsbergen</a> (<a href="https://2023.splashcon.org/committee/sle-2023-program-committee">PC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/MarkvandenBrand.html">Mark van den Brand</a> (<a href="https://2023.splashcon.org/committee/sle-2023-program-committee">PC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/TijsvanderStorm.html">Tijs van der Storm</a> (<a href="https://2023.splashcon.org/committee/sle-2023-program-committee">PC</a>)</li></ul>
